φ(Very Very large)  = φ(Very large)  + Sign(Very Verylarge)  × (fm(Very Very large)  − 0.5fm(Very Verylarge))  = 0.875 + (+1) × 0.5 × 0.5 × 0.5 × 0.5 = 0.9375.
